Before you is a slain Dao. It appears to have been dead for a considerable while, but bears no markings of decay. Its body is gripped down tightly to the circle surrounding it making it impossible to move. As you look around, you see three vacant circles as well. You wonder where the other intended sacrifices area...

Looking down, off the bridge, you notice the water used to cool the energy flowing through the area runs off into the sewers beneath, carrying with it remnants of arcane energy.
